{"tid":1361570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［理性討論727］黎個終極大反轉","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T16:39:47.000Z","uid":154617,"like":23,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e7aeb77ea696412cfb89ed213b052f90bd62b973","tid":1361570,"uid":154617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:40:05.000Z","msg":"有d長，希望各位可以睇晒，再討論<br />\n<br />\n近日元朗班村民同我方都不斷收到唔同消息<br />\n指對方於727將會升級武力、四周破壞<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">小弟覺得咁既風向都想分化同煽動村民仇視示威者</span></strong></strong></span></span><br />\n好似朱凱廸咁講<br />\n何妖講既保家衛族就會變真<br />\n<br />\n好多巴絲已經講左<br />\n就算勇武今次full gear去<br />\n都難敵班村佬，佢地隨時入村拎刀，武器要幾多有幾多<br />\n我地唔可以比勇武受傷<br />\n一個都不能少<br />\n<br />\n再者，就算呢次我地清算左班鄉黑<br />\n佢地有仇必報，住元天屯既巴絲日後必定非常危險<br />\n<br />\n講完係人都知既廢話，入正題<br />\n<br />\n要贏呢場仗，輿論戰係對我方最有利既<br />\n小弟建議黎個大反轉<br />\n設立街站，派下蛇齋餅糭+宣傳單張<br />\n呼籲村民黎同青年直接對話<br />\n文宣方向係有居心不良既人發放假消息、煽動村民鄉黑攻擊青年人、破壞元朗區安寧、呼籲勿盡信流轉既可疑消息<br />\n口號可以係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">青年非搞事  抹黑極可恥</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你想知多D  勿睇TVB</span></strong></span><br />\n小弟文采唔多好，隨口寫幾句<br />\n千祈唔好講光復、清新元朗等字眼<br />\n避免刺激到佢地既神經<br />\n<br />\n想像下班村佬立晒架餐一落黎見到我地派緊檸檬茶<br />\n個反差有幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個夠膽搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阻住阿婆阿伯黎拎野食，一定會比人鬧返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係做到咁理想，可以黎到個終極大反轉<br />\n村佬發現被利用<br />\n咁就少左敵人少左戰線<br />\n專心處理幾大訴求<br />\n而有良心既警察就會發現一直製造混亂既係佢地自己<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論，時間無多，要做就快手"},{"pid":"a52b64647be33746e969315b74de8a26b83e442c","tid":1361570,"uid":154617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3815d557f2f3bd72cb1652254d54bbdcdbffd144","tid":1361570,"uid":9315,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:48:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母唔入村就話姐<br />\n你居然妄想到仲話要用示威者物資派比牛屎佬?"},{"pid":"0c4399d1993b61b185122b39254f32cfe7263173","tid":1361570,"uid":15379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:48:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2b799b32d26bf98dd674e13a17c962d5ac967b28","tid":1361570,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"咁撚鍾意反轉我建議可以拉你老母入元朗比牛屎佬屌  可能會有阻嚇作用"},{"pid":"b85b4f63ea0e7cca1417247877f761fcf5bad969","tid":1361570,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c4399d1993b61b185122b39254f32cfe7263173","tid":1361570,"uid":15379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:48:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"Push你老母個老母<br />\nPush埋你老母出去比人屌就岩架啦"},{"pid":"c08e9303db48e2e05636390d5a40193478f49305","tid":1361570,"uid":236929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"274f9f4b589c860d4da3f053017cfe3a5b044f5b","tid":1361570,"uid":140915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:11.000Z","msg":"膠得滯"},{"pid":"255c215de6ea6d4bff494318b3c26ad98d13690f","tid":1361570,"uid":191072,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"牛屎佬見到你派檸茶會驚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4195a2eef75b3b65197f7e2a5dce5c2db5d2bd7f","tid":1361570,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:52:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1339734/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1339734/page/1</a><br />\n比起光復元朗，我覺得抵制元朗區會比較好<br />\n硬碰硬一定無著數<br />\n鄉黑又唔怕比黑警拉<br />\n比人打死都係賤命一條，無野輸<br />\n我地應該要留返咁多位義士既體力<br />\n用抵制黎減低鄉黑勢力<br />\n<br />\n抵制行動大家可以傾傾，初步諗到少少idea<br />\n1）呼籲同宣傳香港各大市民避免前往元朗區。大量黑社會人士住係元朗區，大家都唔想無啦啦比人扑濕嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）元朗區朋友麻煩報料邊d鋪係鄉黑經營，各位市民食飯買野都唔想有生命威脅嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正皮個D自己睇樓豬開個account就係為左講D乜柒<br />\n你話唔係牛屎佬都冇人信"},{"pid":"b82f52b52489d51622ddab9187697f06f8450ed1","tid":1361570,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"255c215de6ea6d4bff494318b3c26ad98d13690f","tid":1361570,"uid":191072,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:44.000Z","msg":"牛屎佬見到你派檸茶會驚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"仲唔打多你兩錢重既話我就地切腹"},{"pid":"cefe529aec946ef41ab251f3f603959a8bfb329e","tid":1361570,"uid":154617,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3815d557f2f3bd72cb1652254d54bbdcdbffd144","tid":1361570,"uid":9315,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:48:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母唔入村就話姐<br />\n你居然妄想到仲話要用示威者物資派比牛屎佬?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:53:33.000Z","msg":"你打場仗犧牲少少物資算得咩？<br />\n最緊要你出到黎個運動有無用先<br />\n你打完一班牛屎佬出左啖氣<br />\n咁你嬴左d咩？"},{"pid":"4f20b28ff76fec9ffaa0fccbbe7cf7e4a5c86d78","tid":1361570,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:53:40.000Z","msg":"(突發) 有人邀請鄉事派參加元朗727遊行!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361593</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫手推同share<br />\n推到上報 你就可以減低元朗風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f974bcc0585e14b44fb635d8cedee40f335576","tid":1361570,"uid":154617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4195a2eef75b3b65197f7e2a5dce5c2db5d2bd7f","tid":1361570,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:52:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1339734/page